          <h1>EDMBOOTH Cookie Policy</h1>
          <p>This Cookie Policy is intended to inform you how our Website uses a technology called “cookies” and web server logs. This Cookie Policy is intended to assist you in making informed decisions when using our Website. Please take a minute to read and understand the Cookie Policy.</p>
        </hgroup>
